	* building engineering and technical support systems â technical equipment required to provide heating, cooling, ventilation, water heating, lighting, or a combination thereof, of a building or part of a building;
	* total energy efficiency of a building â the calculated amount of primary energy required for the intended use of a building, which includes the energy consumed for heating, cooling, ventilation, water heating, lighting, and other energy;
