The Government of Georgia shall ensure:
* the approval of minimum energy performance requirements for buildings, parts of buildings or building elements;
	* the approval of a comparative methodology for calculating the cost-optimal levels of the minimum energy performance requirements for buildings, parts of buildings or building elements;
	* the approval of the procedure for the development and use of one or more programme(s) for the calculation of energy performance;
